This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as text summarization. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses a neural network architecture for the task. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques for language processing. It could also be classified under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as text summarization is a common task in information retrieval. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses a neural network architecture for the task.
